title: Migrating to AU | Transferring my account to OCE from Garena
body:
Greetings!

Will the transfers from Garena to Oceania happening sometime soon? I searched google and found out there was a transfer before, but it turns out it was already over.  I'd like to bring my account with me since we're migrating to Australia next week. I have a lot of skins and other stuff in which I've purchased using RP. It would be unfortunate if my account will be left behind. {{item:3070}} {{item:3151}} {{item:3070}}
